    <item>
      <title>创造了七大奇迹的战略家警告称，美国科技将落后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/man-who-coined-the-magnificent-seven-warns-us-tech-is-set-to-lag</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行的迈克尔哈特内特警告称，美国大型科技股今年将成为“七大科技股”，他建议投资者应该购买便宜的国际股票，而不是追逐昂贵的美国股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/man-who-coined-the-magnificent-seven-warns-us-tech-is-set-to-lag</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 10:23:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
