      <title>市场预期欧洲央行进一步降息，欧元将进一步下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/ecb-and-fed-policy-split-sets-up-the-euro-for-a-deeper-decline</link>
